  m_Name: The Prodigy
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Seed
  title: The Prodigy
  description: Eminence! Interesting tidings! It appears a young but prodigious painter
    from the slums is gaining significant prominence among the higher echelons of
    society. Many whisper that he shall be the next great master of our age! Better
    still, his elderly benefactor recently passed away. In his grief, the youth seems
    to have found solace in the Beholder. Perhaps we might persuade him to join our
    fold?
  icon: {fileID: 0}
